data.description: **ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT CONTINUE TO SHOW**Newer 2021 construction home located in Ocean Acres at the end of a cul-da-sac! Step into your foyer with 9ft ceilings that lead to your open floor plan! Kitchen boasts an oversized island, quartz countertops with full stainless steel appliances & pantry. Large main bedroom with en-suite bathroom including double sinks, stand up shower & walk-in closet. Basement is a blank slate to make it your own with 8ft. ceilings! Other features include: 2nd floor laundry room, large 120x75 lot, last home on the cul-da-sac, sidewalks, double wide driveway, double car garage ,lots recess lighting and natural light throughout the main living space. Close to Garden State Parkway, beaches, parks & shopping
